full_text: Screened by NARA, 9/21/2023 UNITED STATES DEPARTMENT OF JUSTICE IMMIGRATION AND NATURALIZATION SERVICE 300 North Los Angeles Street Los Angeles, California 90012 File No. A17 181 791 Date: September 14,1970 Betty Pei-Ing Mao c/o Martha N. Morgan, Esq., 99 South Lake Avenue Pasadena, California 91101 L Dear Madam: Reference is made to the deportation proceedings presently pending against you. The hearing in your case has been rescheduled. You are directed to appear before a Special Inquiry Officer at the place, date, and hour shown below. Very truly yours, Special Inquiry Clerk, Special Inquiry Branch 300 North Los Angeles Street Place of hearing Room 8110, at Los Angeles, California 90012 Date and hour of hearing WEDNESDAY, September 30,1970 at 2:30 P.M. CC: Sam I. Feldman, Trial Attorney, Los Angeles, California 90012 CG: Betty Pei-Ing Mao, c/o Philip S. Fogg; 720 So. Rafeel Ave., Pasadena, Calif. 91105 Form I-293 (Rev. 2-20-70)
